Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax a little, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These people would be late\Nfor their own mother's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But I've got somewhere to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting a lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A lovely blue-eyed brunette.\NEvery night she digs her nails into my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Kuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally. There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the cash, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You shitheads are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The cops could be by at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The cash. Do you have it? Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? You got the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be good quality stuff, right?\NShipped straight from the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us the money. Money first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You piece of shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, here it is.\NFifty grand in cold, hard cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now show us the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A real fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good quality, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A higher race, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You could make some\Nreally good drugs with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid that's a trade secret, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. We'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Rick.\N--Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the business, mister. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure working with you guys.\NGlad it worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy too.\NNow we can finally get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the San-Teresa Metropolitan Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards are cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest for\Nkidnapping and human trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This fairy is a Semanian citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On your knees, hands above your heads.\NGet to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! You shithead cops set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite the potty mouth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick, read 'em their rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do the honors, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.\NYou have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that comes out\Nof that foul mouth of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,may be used against you in a court of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the right to a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't afford to pay\None of those meddling shitheads,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be provided a public defender.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So grateful you could cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"You pathetically weak barbarians..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I'm taking the girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no Earth language... Farbani?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The fairy was always meant to come to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your damn mouth, alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, a hyperspace gate\Nappeared in the middle of the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the gate lay a strange world\Nfilled with fairies and monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariaena Island. The city of San-Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is Earth's "front door."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Over two million citizens\Nfrom this other world live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A mixture of different races and\Ndiverse cultures, haves and have-nots...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's newest "city of dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the shadows of all this\Nchaos lurked countless crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs. Prostitution. Weapons smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The San-Teresa Metropolitan Police maintained\Na special unit to deal with these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoba, they found the perp's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--No entry!\N--It was lying on the road in Apple Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Hills? That's two miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Roth, I got three clean hits with a 9mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No way in hell he made it that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was a normal criminal, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of those goddamn aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was being controlled by\Na Semanian wizard, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The perp was speaking in Farbani.\NUsing vocab from their intellectual class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that fairy was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get things in order.\NMatoba, you get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My partner of four years was just killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find him and make him pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order, Sergeant Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about what happened to Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's why you need\Nto get some rest. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to tell his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your report on my desk\Nby 9:00 AM tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I'll wash your car for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need washing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hundred dollars. If you don't pay it,\Nyour car might get banged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Money. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared, {\i1}doreany{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where'd I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up. And appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Semanians, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth may be weak, but there are\Nscary people here. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes, sir," you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kei! Rick's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No... This can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About tomorrow...\NThere's been a change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to go meet a noble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go meet a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A VIP from the Farbani Kingdom\Nis arriving early tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to go meet some alien noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a diplomat's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough detectives\Nwho can speak their language.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks. Let me hunt down\Nthe guy who killed Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The VIP might be involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get them.\NI've already talked to the coast guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bossy bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever been to their world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. I was in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the war, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stuffed inside a transport plane,\Nso I didn't get to see the gate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can see the Mirage Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to rely on information\Nfrom our observation satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But those damn aliens\Ncan tell where the gate is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,just by looking at the wind and tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And do a damn sight better job than we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why the coast guard's always busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we wanted to catch all\Nthe smugglers and illegal immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd need twice the funding and manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some important noble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A child? A servant, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the VIP?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Exedilica, of the Knights of Mirvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do Earth sailors not even\Nhave the ritual of welcoming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not know how to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer me. Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna Barsh Mirvor Imsedalya Iyeh\NTebreina Devol Nelano Seiya Nel Exedilica!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In your Earth language, that means
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tilarna, eldest daughter of Seiya,\Nof the House of Exedilica,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,heir to the bloodline of Duke Devol,\Nof the glorious Knights of Mirvor."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now. What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kei Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, people of low birth often have short names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually go by Tilarna Exedilica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, carry my things, Kay Imatuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. Start carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not hear me, Sergeant Matoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be working with her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be doing your investigations with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll take Sergeant Fury's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to work with this alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's racist, Sergeant Matoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. He doesn't understand\Nthe circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She came here to find that fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a {\i1}fiel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fiel queze badeley{\i0}. It means "most noble fairy."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That fairy is the equivalent\Nof a VIP in the Semani world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was kidnapped there\Nand brought here by smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Farbanian knight\Nsent here to recover the fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with our treaty with\Nthe country called "The United Nations,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the Knights of Mirvor are given\Nthe right to dispense justice on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Tilarna Exedilica, request your help\Nin the name of the Farbani Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bullshit! Rick was my partner\Nfor four years, and now he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm supposed to babysit some kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your order can go eat shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Roth, don't you want\Nto avenge Rick? This is just--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known Rick for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to do this\Nbecause it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need any more explanation than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that my own will is being ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to work with the best "boliceman"\Nyour city has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine a rude boor\Nlike this acting as my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. We can find another...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he'll be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want a man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,whose etiquette is perfect,\Nbut who's otherwise completely useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Roth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I don't think you'll\Nbe getting your fairy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What've we got, Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked. He was too scared\Nto say much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That fairy was stolen, supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,From a gang of Mexicans in a Ridgeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like he doesn't know their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to find the fairy's original owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There can't be that many Mexican gangs\Nin Ridgelines running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Ridgeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Mexican?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A person from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Just shut up and sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rakebye{\i0}! Are you trying to get me killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just don't do anything!\NDon't touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you, Kay Imatuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to walk as far away\Nfrom me as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone thinking we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence. Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we don't open until seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenny, is O'Neill in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the other room on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time with her, then.\NI'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He can go in, but you're not welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you not hear me? Turn around and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around and what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on in, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd get scared and beg for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this should be a good deal for us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This gift of 50 51-inch TVs\Nbrought to us by these sinful
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,young children is truly a blessing from God.\NFor the Lord sayeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no TVs.\NIt's a theological analogy for God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got visitors.\NBlessings of God be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Matoba!\NFeeling the breath of God today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's the beautiful lady with you?\NWelcome to my house of faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Neill, I'm looking for a Mexican gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They drive a Ridgeline.\NProbably transporters. Know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a violent bunch, and I'd rather\Nnot anger them if possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps a sufficiently large\Ndonation could make God
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,whisper something to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A donation of around\N300 dollars, specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to deal with\Nthe goddess of the courtroom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and her sword and scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on probation, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an illegal threat, Sergeant Matoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday Satan will get his claws into your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan can suck my dick.\NNow, what's this about 51-inch TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go ask the guys\Nin the burglary division?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're willing to believe the words of a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Neill may be a criminal,\Nbut he doesn't like drugs or murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be trusted... to a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a guy you just can't hate, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Aren't you supposed\Nto be enforcers of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that there were warriors on Earth\Nwho fought for the cause of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That they helped the needy and fought evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you "bolicemen" are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly had some hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe you're\Nmaking deals with a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have no pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, you'd be right, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,581 Mason Street. Room 603.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Antonio Alvarez. You need backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. If there's no word from me in 30 minutes,\Nthen you can worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I should've known you wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of {\i1}latena{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone controlled by\Nan evil wizard was just here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shield of law, protection of the war god."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next time"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}COP CRAFT{\i0}.
